BodyText: Hey dude. I am actually not too sure how that side of the house is structured, but I know a lot of them still use @dlt email addresses so its difficult for us to search aliases or org charts. I know Catherine Jones just moved over to that team, so maybe ping her and see if she knows who you can work with. Otherwise, I found dlt@tdsynnex.com that might be able to help run with that one.
